WEBVTT

1
00:49:56.730 --> 00:49:57.860 
- 他追上来了 - 让一让，让一让
- ALVIN: He's coming! - MILES: Watch out, gangway!

2
00:49:57.890 --> 00:49:59.220 
快点，喜多，快
Hurry, Theodore, run!

3
00:49:59.260 --> 00:50:00.960 
- 快点，伙计们，快点 - 请让一下
Let's go! Come on, hurry up! Excuse us!

4
00:50:00.990 --> 00:50:02.530 
- 快点，艾文，他追上来了 - 快点，迈尔斯
Come on, Alvin! He's coming! Go, Miles, go!

5
