- 总算甩掉他了 - 嘿
Whoo, I think we lost him. Hey!

7
00:50:09.660 --> 00:50:10.660 
别听艾文的
SIMON: Disregard.

8
00:50:10.690 --> 00:50:11.530 
给我回来
Come back here!

9
00:50:13.990 --> 00:50:15.190 
不好意思，借过
Excuse me, pardon me.

10
00:50:15.230 --> 00:50:16.230 
有个疯子在追我们
There's a crazy guy chasing us!

11
00:50:20.390 --> 00:50:23.590 
瞧你精疲力尽的，宝贝儿 拿去喝吧
You look tired, baby. Here you go.

12
00:50:23.630 --> 00:50:24.390 
太感谢了
Oh, thank you so much.

